		<item>
		<title>מה יהיה הנושא השבועי??</title>
		<link>http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/?p=3809&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=%25d7%259e%25d7%2594-%25d7%2599%25d7%2594%25d7%2599%25d7%2594-%25d7%2594%25d7%25a0%25d7%2595%25d7%25a9%25d7%2590-%25d7%2594%25d7%25a9%25d7%2591%25d7%2595%25d7%25a2%25d7%2599-3</link>
